G

generate() - Method in class Apriori
Given a set of k-frequent item sets Fk = { fk | fk is frequent and |f| = k}, we generate the candidate frequent item sets C = { l union m | l, m belong to F and l != m and l intersection m belongs Fk-1 and there does not exist a subset of l union m, of size k, that belongs to F}.
